[normal]For example, since one primary Free School in Haringey started offering an extended day, a number of local primaries have 
[normal]followed suit
[normal]. Similarly, since a Free School was approved to open on the Isle of Wight next year offering pupils Latin, several local
[normal] secondary schools have also decided to offer it.
